For highborn, you folk sure
do some decent things for
your people, doncha?

rows.label: tlk70000059_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I always imagined you blue-bloods
would have your heads too far up
your own arses to think of others.

rows.label: tlk70000059_05_msg0003
rows.name:
This has been a real eye-opener for me,
let me tell you. I feel like I've learnt
a "valuable" fact from all this.

rows.label: tlk70000059_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Yes, indeed, I'll have to "invest"
in your talents a whole lot more
from now on, darlings! â™ª
